Subject: [PATCH] drm/radeon: Add a common function for DFS handling
Mime-version: 1.0
Content-type: text/plain; charset=UTF-8
Content-transfer-encoding: 8bit
Git-commit: a64c9dab1c4d05c87ec8a1cb9b48915816462143
Patch-mainline: 4.5-rc2
References: boo#955096,boo#967938

Move encoding of DFS (digital frequency synthesizer) divider into a
separate function and improve calculation precision.

